>[!hint] Use the Azure credentials provided in the hosted VM to complete this lab, not the Learn sandbox. 

## Lab: Explore Azure SQL Database

As part of your role at Contoso as a data engineer, you've been asked to create and configure SQL Server, PostgreSQL, and MySQL servers for Azure.

In this lab you'll create and configure a server for Azure SQL Server. If you have time later, you can use this lab to create and configure servers for Azure PostgreSQL and MySQL.

1.	Go to the Microsoft Learn exercise at https://docs.microsoft.com/learn/modules/explore-provision-deploy-relational-database-offerings-azure/4-exercise-provision-relational-azure-data-services?pivots=azuresql#provision-an-azure-sql-database-resource and follow the instructions in the browser.
